Tidak, bukan disebut-sebut,
tetapi dikritik.

937
00:54:45,253 --> 00:54:47,588
Dikritik habis-habisan.

938
00:54:47,672 --> 00:54:49,257
"Kenapa tim dokter bedah saraf?"

939
00:54:50,133 --> 00:54:52,677
