karena kau yang salah.

953
00:55:28,504 --> 00:55:29,797
Itu yang benar saat ini.

954
00:55:30,548 --> 00:55:31,466
Baik.

955
00:55:31,549 --> 00:55:34,344
Lekas keluar. Nanti kutraktir minum bir.

956
00:55:35,011 --> 00:55:35,845
Baik.

957
00:55:37,055 --> 00:55:38,139
Terima kasih.

958
00:55:41,976 --> 00:55:42,977
Astaga.

959
00:55:44,270 --> 00:55:45,146
Astaga.

