00:55:48,775 --> 00:55:50,151
Hei, Lee Ik-jun.

961
00:55:50,526 --> 00:55:51,861
Ada apa, Kim Jun-wan?

962
00:55:53,196 --> 00:55:54,322
Kakimu!

963
00:55:55,281 --> 00:55:56,157
Kenapa?

964
00:55:56,991 --> 00:55:58,034
